      • initialize

        public void initialize​(java.net.URL url,
                       java.util.ResourceBundle resourceBundle)
        Initializes the page. LAMBDA expression to handle the selection of the country from the country combo box. I needed this LAMBDA as it made the process for assigning the selection to the variable much easier than any other way to do it. Also, I was able to incorporate a few other steps with one simple LAMBDA Method. Specifically the ability to also filter down the first level divisions box to only the relevant states/providences/regions.
        Specified by:
        initialize in interface javafx.fxml.Initializable
        Parameters:
        url -
        resourceBundle -
